defaultThe HS1 sale process has been a success generating £2.1bn in income for the taxpayer in 2010 with the opportunity to realise further taxpayer benefit in 2040.  It provides a framework for on-going delivery of important railway infrastructure services of benefit to UK plc. Significant 
defaultprivate investment such as that delivered by our shareholders relies on the existence of an independent regulatory body – such as the ORR. 
